snippet: Rasel Siddiquee, 27, was arrested at Kennedy Airport in connection with the grisly death of Mahuddin Mahmud.
abstract: Rasel Siddiquee, 27, is arrested at Kennedy Airport in connection with grisly death of Mahuddin Mahmud; Siddiquee was a tenant in building owned by victim, who was killed with a sword; relatives found Mahmud's nearly decapitated and partly burned body in basement of building he owned in Kensington neighborhood of Brooklyn.
lead_paragraph: Rasel Siddiquee, 27, was arrested at Kennedy Airport in connection with the grisly death of Mahuddin Mahmud.

headline.main: Man Arrested at Kennedy in Killing of Landlord
headline.print_headline: Man Arrested at Kennedy in Killing of Landlord
